    public interface IDclfAlgoLookup
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'IDclf Algo Lookup'. DclfAlgo object id -> DclfAlgoBus/DclfAlgoBranch, object name -> DclfAlgoGen/DclfAlgoLoad interface
